d[67004]={de="Our efforts have created everything we need to open an Earth-Warder's Vault. There are several beneath the Citadel. Locate one and I will reward you. I have crafted chains to help move it. If you bring the Vault here, we can share in the riches. Watch for the Vault being moved, as I have dispatched others to find them as well."}
d[67031]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67032]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67034]={de="To the east is a great dragonspring which serves as a nesting area for wild eagles. The feathers they shed still contain their magic for quite some time and are used in many rituals. The area also hosts raging spirits of the elements, and their cores are of some use as well. Bring a collection of both back to me - and remember that the eagles are sacred, I will not accept feathers that are gathered from their harm."}
d[67039]={de="A few of the clan's pets ended up getting lost along the last journey between camps. They're not hunting animals so I doubt they can take care of themselves properly out there! Do you think you could go search for them? They may not be hunting partners, but they're important members of the clan regardless!"}
d[67095]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67096]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67222]={de="The Primalists have infected Windsong Rise with their nonsense teachings. Our kin there are foolish to entertain their ideas. If we assist with clearing this sacred ground of their presence, perhaps the other clans will come to our aid in time of need. Do you think you could assist?"}
d[67296]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67297]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67565]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67566]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67605]={de="There is a great storm beast which wanders this ridge. Many a Shikaar hunter has attempted to take it down, only to fall to its ferocity. If you wish for some hunting glory, you may attempt to bring down the beast. Bring back its horn as tribute."}
d[67741]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[67742]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[69925]={de="These Primalists are relentless, unleashing elemental devastation across the Eastern Kingdoms and Kalimdor. You must show the same determination, {name}. It is the only way to stop them. Find their next incursion, remove the enemies within the primal storm area before it is too late and foil their efforts. We must protect Azeroth!"}
d[69937]={de="Ah, {name}, there you are! I've been looking all over for you. Another of our local critters has been suffering from a distinct lack of affectionate treat-feeding of late. Won't you go and find them something sweet to snack on?"}
d[69957]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[69958]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[70049]={de="These Primalists are relentless, unleashing elemental devastation across the Eastern Kingdoms and Kalimdor. You must show the same determination, {name}. It is the only way to stop them. Find their next incursion, remove the enemies within the primal storm area before it is too late and foil their efforts. We must protect Azeroth!"}
