d[75466]={de="Some rowdy customers stumbled out of a temporal portal a bit ago. Before I could get a Timewalker to help get them home, they decided to visit Valdrakken. Would you find Olaf, Baelog, and Eric and get them to come back here before they cause too much of a ruckus?"}
d[75657]={de="We have a teensy problem I could use your help with. But it's... complicated. Some time ago, King Varian Wrynn was in a gladiator trio with Broll Bearmantle and Valeera Sanguinar. Those three just showed up in this 'Field of Ferocity' place and they're not only taking on all challengers, they're beating them too! They won't return through our portals until they lose. Do you think you could find some friends and defeat them? We'll be able to convince them to go back if you can, I'm sure of it!"}
