d[75970]={de="A Timewalker spotted a bear cub who stumbled into our present time. She was so frightened she ran off before he could catch her! Can you find the poor thing? You'll need to calm her down before she'll follow you. Bring her back here and I'll open a temporal portal to take her home."}
d[75971]={de="We have detected another time anomaly. A strange object that even we cannot understand the significance of. This artifact must be returned before it does irreparable damage to the true timeline and the world as we know it. Return here once you have recovered the artifact. I will open a portal so you may return it to its proper place."}
