d[77426]={de="Interested in trying to get a faster time? [Eruption]: Dash forward. [Rock Halt]: Stops forward movement. [Earthen Will]: Restores all Vigor. Must be grounded."}
d[77427]={de="Interested in trying to get a faster time? [Growth Spurt]: Tranform into an adult and gain improved speed. [Bedtime Rewind]: Restore 1 Vigor until all Vigor has been recovered. [Sacred Timeline]: Resets cooldowns."}
d[77428]={de="Interested in trying to get a faster time? [Blink Boost]: Blink forward and dash. [Arcane Acceleration]: Increases forward acceleration. [Accelerated Restoration]: Consumes Arcane Acceleration and restores Vigor."}
d[77429]={de="Interested in trying to get a faster time? [Nature's Wind]: Fly up then restore 1 Vigor. [Emerald Restraint]: Adds 5 sec to Winds of Life's duration. [Winds of Life]: Anytime you restore Vigor, dash forward."}
d[77430]={de="Interested in trying to get a faster time? [Ruby Exhaustion]: Consumes all Vigor over time. [Crimson Flight]: Restore all Vigor, boosting forward each time. [Renewal]: Consumes Crimson Flight, resets cooldowns."}
