d[77653]={de="Here for the latest? Well, have I got news for you. A weaponsmith was just here visiting Tithris. Koref, I think? Couldn't help but overhear their discussion about some sort of ancient key. Might be of interest to you, what with all your artifact hunting. Weaponsmith Koref was headed back to the Obsidian Enclave. You should head there and get the scoop about this ancient key."}
