d[78565]={de="Today's special is a magical getaway to the majestic forests of Northrend! Say, you're one of those adventurers, right? Listen, I need a favor. Could you pick me a few flowers from Grizzly Hills? I've got my hands full here, but there's someone I'd really like to give a bouquet to."}
d[78591]={de="Today's special is a magical getaway to the great plains of Nagrand! If you're headed there, would you mind shooting a few animals? Oh, not like that! Here, borrow my camera. My friend Beatrice has been roaming around there lately. She would really appreciate some photographs, but I've got portals to attend to."}
d[78594]={de="Today's special is a magical getaway to the sunny beaches of Feralas! The Steam Pools resort is having a lovely celebration and all are invited! Unfortunately, some of the partygoers who took this portal earlier left their gifts here at the gala. Could you help me return them? Meet me at the beach and we'll figure out which gifts belong to whom."}
d[78608]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[78609]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[78610]={de="Fly through the checkpoint rings marking the course."}
d[78674]={de="You adventurers are known to carry heavy burdens. There will be no better time to confront them than now. I saw a veteran somewhere around here. There is a chance he may know what it means to cope with stress. Perhaps he has insight to teach you."}
d[78679]={de="Self-love can take many different forms. And on occasion it can take the form of relaxing. The night elf by the fireworks seems particularly relaxed. Perhaps you could ask him for his insights on relaxation."}
d[78724]={de="If it's a challenge you're after, I think I have an idea. I saw a boastful champion heading toward Goldshire. You could challenge him to a duel. This would satisfy your desire and perhaps teach him a valuable lesson in humility."}
d[78726]={de="A full belly is a happy belly! There is plenty of good food and drink right here at the gala. Why don't you buy yourself something nice?"}
d[78938]={de="I regret to inform you that a horrific threat awaits your kind within this mortal realm. An Elemental Lord of Fire, Ragnaros, bides his time waiting to strike and burn your Azeroth to its core. We, the elements of water, have waged war eternal with those beings of the lesser elementals. Trust that our warning is no small thing. Prove your conviction! Slay Ragnaros, once and for all!"}
d[78979]={de="While visiting this gala, I am staying at the Razor Hill inn. It may not look like much, but it is surprisingly comfortable! Why don't you see if they have any extra beds you could use? I think I will have a bit of a rest too... Right... here..."}
d[78986]={de="Good morrow! Today's special portal is a magical getaway to the majestic forests of Northrend! Although perhaps I could beg you for a favor. You seem the adventurous type. I could use your help in delivering some flowers from Grizzly hills to a beautiful woman named Laverne. I would do it myself but... Well, you see, she is rather intimidating in her beauty."}
d[78987]={de="Good morrow! Today's special portal is a magical getaway to the great plains of Nagrand! Would you, perchance, be interested in a proposition? I will lend you my camera if you could deliver any photographs you take to my dear friend Karn. He has been adrift in Nagrand as of late, lost in his own thoughts. As stubborn as he is, I'm sure he will appreciate the company. I would do it myself, but I must maintain the portals here."}
d[78988]={de="Good morrow! Today's special portal is a magical getaway to the sunny beaches of Feralas! The Steam Pools resort is having a lovely celebration and all are invited! Unfortunately, some of our festival attendees who took this portal earlier left their gifts here at the gala. Could you perchance help me return them? I will meet you at the beach and together we shall be able to determine which gifts belong to whom."}
d[78990]={de="You adventurers are known to carry heavy burdens. There will be no better time to confront them than now. I saw a veteran somewhere around here. There is a chance he may know what it means to cope with stress. Perhaps he has insight to teach you."}
d[78991]={de="Love is a gift, yes. But it is also a gift that you can give yourself. Sometimes, the best way to love yourself is simply to relax. I met a troll across the Southfury River who seems particularly wise in this regard. Perhaps you could ask her for insights in the art of relaxation."}
d[79135]={de="Those dratted ducks! Do you mind scaring them off again? I simply cannot leave my golden egg unattended!"}
